{"tid":2311102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「希特拉」宣布贏出大選","createTime":"2020-12-03T21:06:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T12:30:01.000Z","uid":28114,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"445a4e9d229713c104c184e0dc87e84c84b2af1a","tid":2311102,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T21:06:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X3JC9KT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX3JC9KT.jpg&h=77ec09f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAdolf Hitler has won a seat in a Namibian election. Yes, you read that right, the politician&rsquo;s name really is Adolf Hitler &ndash; Adolf Hitler Uunona to be exact.<br />\n<br />\nSo, how did his name come to be? Well, according to Adolf, his father had named him Hitler without realizing what the name meant.<br />\n<br />\n&lsquo;My father named me after this man. He probably didn&rsquo;t understand what Adolf Hitler stood for,&rsquo; he said. &lsquo;As a child, I saw it as a totally normal name. Only as a teenager did I understand that this man wanted to conquer the whole world.&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\nNamibia is a former German colony, where a number of streets, places, and people still bear German names. But there&rsquo;s no German name quite as striking as Adolf. Thankfully, Namibia&rsquo;s own does not have any plans for global domination. <br />\n<br />\nHe also promises he wants &lsquo;nothing to do with Nazi ideology.&rsquo;<br />\n<br />\nREAD MORE: <a href=\"https://on.rt.com/aweu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fon.rt.com%2Faweu&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGBfhc2i76iEVsdTpjF8%2BTp8%3D&h=8b0046c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://on.rt.com/aweu</a>"},{"pid":"33ca2730e25310cc0594c0cd1e175a1ed5ddbd26","tid":2311102,"uid":28114,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T21:06:58.000Z","msg":"真係希特拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b77db452fe8a29c9a104849e